body:
Underappreciated part of detective Pikachu

The scene where Justice’s character is fighting the ditto and the ditto transforms into the girl. He says that he is kinda attracted to instead of in love with. I find myself thinking, ‘that’s fair’ also they didn’t kiss in the movie it’s just implied he might have gotten a date. Not every movie needs a kiss, I appreciate that.

body:
Saw detective pikachu yesterday

I feel like it did awesome subtle red herring/expectation shift by showing a news article of Mew and when Tim is begging Bulbasaur to help Pikachu, I totally thought it would take them to Mew…so it got honest “holy shit” out of me when helper didn’t turn out to be mew :D
